    --- Returns: String.
    --- Summary: Renders the <a> HTML element.
    --- Contract: Preserve this typed interface when upgrading to a runtime-backed implementation.
    function A(attrs : List[String], children : String) : String {
        return Element("a", attrs, children);
    }

